{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_deepcl_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_deepcl_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"幽蓝怀想","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"一位古怪的画家生活在小镇。某天，一位不速之客到访。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_deepcl_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["画店店主","奇怪的外来人","怪异的画家","外来的教士","担心的镇民","大胆的镇民","其余镇民"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1c/Avg_bg_27_g16_lighthouse_street.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":12},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"您好，先生，本店还没有到开门的时间，请下午再来吧。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"很抱歉我来得不是时候，但我来到此地并非为了购买画作，只是为了向您打听些事。","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"冒昧来访，还请收下薄礼。","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"（从袖中摸出金币塞入门缝）","id":18,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"这是......","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"一点心意而已，如果您能帮到我，还会有更多财物用以答谢您的付出。","id":22,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"character","id":24},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":25},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_178","fadetime":"1","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":27},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"啊，很荣幸见到您，店主先生。","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"嗯咳......这位先生您有什么事需要帮忙？","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"在上个月，一幅我珍若生命的的画作因为保存不当受潮严重，随后油彩大片脱落。","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"我恰好听闻此地有一位绘匠技艺精湛，善于修补，所以才找到此地碰碰运气，希望她能够挽救此画。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"这......恐怕有些难度，那个人并不好找。","id":36},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"莫非她住的地方离镇子还有些距离？我这里还有些多余的金币。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"（再从袖子中摸出几枚金币）","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"并非如此，她就住在镇子里，只是她这个人性格古怪，从没人敢轻易靠近。","id":41},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"她脾气暴烈，常常出手伤人？或者孤僻高傲，总是难以亲近？","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"事实上，她......称得上热情活泼。","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"哦？","id":47,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"她自己留在屋里作画还好，最多也就是会从屋内传出怪声，但当她出门写生时......大家都对她避之不及，生怕自己成为她的参照模特。","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"只要被她盯上，再怎么推脱也没用，哪怕有要事，也只能坐下等她画完。","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"您也知道，作画不是立刻就能完成的，一坐下一天的时间都耽误了。","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"为什么不拒绝呢？","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"拒绝......？","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"对啊......为什么没有人拒绝？为什么没人能拒绝？","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"（神情恍惚地喃喃自语）","id":57},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"先生、店主先生，您还好吗？","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"没、没事......适才我回想了下她曾经和我说过些什么，但是脑子里乱糟糟的，什么也想不起来。","id":61},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"这还真是古怪......呵呵。","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"算了，她这人疯疯癫癫，怪话连篇，记不得也没有关系。","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"如果先生您在和她相处的过程中有觉得被冒犯的地方，还请不要放在心上。","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"呵呵，想不到您居然会维护这样一位古怪的画家。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"她来到这里后虽然行为举止怪异，但是也从来没有伤害过这里的人，更何况......","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"更何况我们店里挂在墙壁上的，有一半都是她的画作，很受顾客欢迎。","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"真是勤奋高产的绘匠啊，呵呵。真是让我更加好奇了。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"先生，既然您坚持，那请您跟我来吧，我带您去找她。","id":75},{"type":"dialog","id":76},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"character","id":79},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_bg_27_g17_lighthouse_alley.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":80},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":81},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":83},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","fadetime":"1.5","id":84},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":85},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"她就住在这间房子里，我还有事情，就带您到这里了。","id":87},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"您不愿陪我一起进去吗？","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"这......先生，我还有事，还是不奉陪了。","id":91},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"那就谢谢您了。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"（从袖子里抓出一大把金币）","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"这是您的报酬。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"谢谢！谢谢！先生您实在是太客气了！如果您还有需要办的事情，可以去店里找我。","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"再见了，店主先生。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_178","focus":"2","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"哎？好好，先生再见。","id":101},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":103},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"真是藏了一个好地方啊。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":108},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":109},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"character","id":112},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c7/Avg_bg_bg_ibindoor.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":114},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":115,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":117},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":119},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":121},{"type":"text","text":"已经快到中午，本应是光线充足的时刻。","id":122},{"type":"text","text":"可房间内门窗紧闭，阳光只能从钉在窗户上的几块木板之间进入，勉强让房间不至于陷入完全的黑暗之中。","id":123},{"type":"text","text":"从最幽暗的角落，几声细微的刮擦声传入外来者的耳中。","id":124},{"type":"text","text":"他整整袍子，走上前去，见到一面巨大的画板立在地上，一个女人举起画笔在上面铺叠着色彩。","id":125},{"type":"dialog","id":126},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","fadetime":"1.5","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":128},{"type":"multiline","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你觉得我应该把笔尖攥得更干一些，但那样刷痕就太明显了，我不喜欢......","id":129},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#7$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":130},{"type":"multiline","name":"怪异的画家","end":"true","text":"不，这不是我想要呈现色彩的方式。","id":131},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#7$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"看，这样更好不是吗？","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f6/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"颜色可以在画布上延展得更远，我必须一笔涂抹到底，不能中断......不能，坚决不能。","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"......","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"好久不见了......","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#4$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"嗯......？","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"啊，原来是你，请坐吧。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奇怪的外来人","text":"你有多久没有清理过这里了，这面镜子已经照不出任何的事物了。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#8$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"哈哈哈，教士先生，你是在嫌弃我肮脏破败的小屋吗？你不知道，在这里，我可以迸发出不计其数的灵感。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/04/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你还是和以前一样，除了自己的艺术，其他什么都不在乎。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你倒是变了很多，从前你的眉头不会皱这么紧。","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"是吗......","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你陷入苦恼了吗？","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"......","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你不想说就算了。","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"想起初次见到你的时候，你也像现在一样，沉醉在作画中。","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#7$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你初次见我？那是什么时候的事了，太久远了，记不清了。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f6/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"那天，你和使者初次见面，我就在那块礁石后面。","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"原来那时你也在海岸边......我只记得使者向我展露的美，我从未见过那样美丽的生物。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"我想，使者也感受到了你的仰慕，仅仅一次简单的接触过后，就引领你走向大群，成为我们的同胞。","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#8$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我始终感激。","id":170,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/04/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"但你却在距离海洋只有一步之遥的地方掉头折返。","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我无意辩解。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你背离族群，伤害同胞，只是为了完成这幅画作吗？","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"（手指抚上画布）","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"如此美丽，却背负上如此的罪恶。","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我深感抱歉。","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"可你的歉意也并未让你的画笔有过丝毫停顿。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"唉，你太固执，太狭隘，将自己拘束在画布之中，看不到遥远的未来。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你不理解族群也不适合族群，既然你始终无法融入，那便应当被清理，成为族群的养分。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"这才是你最应有的归宿，我很遗憾，但也欣喜。同胞，我们终将成为一体。","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"（抖抖袖子）","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你介意收起那东西，多等一会儿吗？我想在一切结束前把它完成。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"（整整袖口）","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"我花了很长时间来到这里，不在乎短短片刻。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"那就好。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"正好，在终结你的生命之前，我也有些话想要问你。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"可以，但我的画笔不会停止。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"为什么......你要选择离开我们？","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"在族群中生命永存，我们彼此之间亲密相连，一同分担你的喜怒忧乐。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"呵......你们所说的分担，不过是变相剥夺我所有的情绪，让我沦为族群生存意志的复诵者。","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你的情绪宣泄毫无意义，它无法平息你的怒火，也无法消弭你的悲伤，只会让你在无限的惊惧中沉沦，一步步走向灭亡。","id":204,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"为了族群，我们将赘余的过激情绪封存，持续的紧张状态不利于族群的生存延续。","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你应该主动舍弃，同我们一道拥抱平静与安宁，不再被自己的情绪左右。","id":206,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#5$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"可是......作为一个艺术家，我的悲鸣、呐喊和嘶吼都是我创作的养料。","id":208,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/ca/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我融入你们的原因从来不是追求平静安宁。","id":210,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你到底希望从我们身上得到什么呢？","id":212,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"融入或者离开，在我眼里，最渴求的东西从未改变。","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"美，永恒的美，栖息在一切生命之中的美。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"难道你没有得到吗？","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"使者的美不过向你显露了片刻，便已足够撼动你的终生，你还不能满足吗？","id":218,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"使者甚至在你的体内留下了种子，令你成为我们的同类，共享美丽。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"是啊，你们身体内蕴藏着的，是超越一切的终极之美。","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"但你们可曾在意过，欣赏过？","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你们所做的每一次选择，都将你们导向永恒的艺术，但面对艺术，你们却始终无动于衷。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"面对生存与进化的诘问，你们选择抛弃对美的认知。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"而我在融入你们的过程中，也变得越来越麻木，不再创作，也不再欣赏。","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你不知道当我发现自己的画笔已经落满尘埃时的心情......那一刻的痛苦让我意识到自己必须离开族群。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"原来是这样......你还是无法割舍人类的欲望。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"人类创造艺术，不过是表达自我的方式；人类欣赏艺术，也不过是从中寻找自我。","id":232,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"自始至终，不过是对镜自怜。","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"多么自私，多么可悲......","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"（放下画笔）","id":236,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你完成了。","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"是的，我完成了。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"蓝色，满目的蓝色。你既已见过海洋的深邃，就应该明白在画布的方寸之间，无法承载磅礴汹涌的巨浪。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你在上面看到了海......可我笔下描绘的，只是一捧水。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"水的命运从海洋开始，亦终结于海洋。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"那也是水的命运，不是海的。","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你既已落下最后一笔，那就该动身离开了。","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我耗费数月，日夜不眠，终于在今天完成了它。你来的时间正好，作为它的第一位观赏者，或许应该再多看看。","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"对于我们而言，这只是一张铺满色块的布而已，它没有任何意义。","id":254,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"布？你错了，你常说我的目光拘泥于画布之上，看不到真正的伟大，而你......你又何尝不是如此呢？","id":256,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"什么？","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":259},{"type":"dialog","id":260},{"type":"character","id":261},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"50","fadetime":"3.5","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":264,"musicid":2},{"type":"text","text":"顷刻间，房间内所有物体的表面都自行剥落，露出底下的颜色——一种怪异的蓝色。","id":265},{"type":"text","text":"更准确来说，是一种像生物般开始吞噬四周颜色的蓝色。","id":266},{"type":"text","text":"很快，这些四处游走的颜色遍布了整个房屋，甚至连窗板间的缝隙也填满了浓烈的蓝色，将阳光彻底阻隔在室外。","id":267},{"type":"text","text":"而本应彻底陷入黑暗的房间内却变得异常明亮，只有蓝色，满目的蓝色。","id":268},{"type":"text","text":"闪烁着不祥光芒的蓝色，充斥着森然杀机的蓝色。","id":269},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"啊......原来如此，这才是你作品的全貌。","id":273,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"是我低估了你......这半年来你进步太多。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"回去吧，教士先生，就当作从未见过我，你已经错过了逮捕我的最好时机。","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"真是可惜......","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你不该有那么多问题，猎杀与捕食从来不需多言，行动就够了。","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"自始至终，你就不应该孤身来找我。","id":282,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"原来是这样......","id":284,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"是什么？","id":286,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"这些年，我始终都无法进行下一步的蜕变，为此我困扰了很久，一直试图寻找原因。","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"现在看来......我也有些属于人类的欲望。好奇心，大概这就是我无法进一步蜕变的原因吧......","id":289,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"似乎你也在同一个地方停下了，不论你自己的意愿如何，总有些属于人类的东西如影随形，无法抛弃。","id":291,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"呵......真是可悲。","id":293,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"离开这里吧，教士先生，你和我一样，无法成为它们，所以也像我一样，逃离吧。","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"......","id":297,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"......不。","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":299},{"type":"character","id":300},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":301},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":302},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magic_2","volume":"1","id":303},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":305},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"嘶——你这家伙还不死心。","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你能对我造成的伤害，也就只有这点皮肉伤罢了。","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":309},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"......该死。","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你在我身上留下了什么？","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"一个小小的“标记”而已。","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你现在比我强大太多，我无法独自将你清除，但总有同胞可以。这个“标记”将为他们指引道路，只要你还在呼吸，“标记”便会永远闪烁。","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我给过你机会了......教士先生。","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"你既然选择逃离，那便永远逃离吧。","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"而我已经来到末路，再无前进的可能，那便永远地留在路途之中吧。","id":322,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"外来的教士","text":"而我的遗体亦会成为后来者的养分，他们将比我走得更远。","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_npc_454_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#6$1","blackstart":"0.15","blackend":"0.45","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我尊重你的选择......","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":326},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":327},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"-1","xstrength":"3","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"10","randomness":"30","block":"false","id":328},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"50","fadetime":"3.5","block":"true","id":329},{"type":"text","text":"在外来者的双眼中，所有的蓝色开始扭曲，它们挣扎着脱离原本附着的地方。","id":330},{"type":"text","text":"大量的黏液掉在地板上，扭动着向外来者靠近，沾湿了他的袍角，顺着他的袍子不断向上攀附。","id":331},{"type":"dialog","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-300","fadetime":"5","isblock":"false","id":334},{"type":"character","fadetime":"2.5","id":335},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":336},{"type":"camerashake","stop":"true","id":337},{"type":"text","text":"将他紧紧包围的同时，股股黏液聚合成细条，逐渐变粗，最终形成一只只触手将动弹不得的他淹没。","id":338},{"type":"text","text":"最后留在他逐渐模糊视线中的，只有一个女人怜悯的双眼。","id":339},{"type":"dialog","id":340},{"type":"character","id":341},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":342},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","volume":"1","id":343},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":344},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":346},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#2$1","fadetime":"1","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我们的道路只是短暂交叠，你却以为我们在行同一条道路。","id":349,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"你以为我是逃离，但其实我只是走到了分岔路。","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"我的前路，依然可追。","id":351,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"再见了......","id":352,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#1$1","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"......看来，这里是没法继续待了。","id":354,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_110_deepcl_1#5$1","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怪异的画家","text":"在哪里可以不被打扰呢......","id":356,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/ca/Avg_avg_110_deepcl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":357},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":358},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"character","id":361},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1c/Avg_bg_27_g16_lighthouse_street.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":362},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":363},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":364,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":366},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_explo_n","volume":"1","id":367},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":368},{"type":"playsound","key":"$a_bat_buildingshaking_1","volume":"1","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":370},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":371},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":372},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":373},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担心的镇民","text":"刚刚那一声巨响是怎么回事？","id":375},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大胆的镇民","text":"哎，你也听到了？刚刚在屋子里听到就赶紧出来了。","id":377},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担心的镇民","text":"啊，这一片废墟是......绘匠的家？","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担心的镇民","text":"怎么会突然就坍塌了？","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担心的镇民","text":"我今天......没看到她出门，搞不好是被埋在底下了。","id":381},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大胆的镇民","text":"你快去多喊些帮手来清理！","id":383},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担心的镇民","text":"哎，好。","id":385},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大胆的镇民","text":"喂，绘匠，你在底下吗？能听到我的声音吗？","id":387},{"type":"dialog","id":388},{"type":"character","id":389},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":390},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":391},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":392},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":393},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_178","fadetime":"1","id":394},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"怎么回事？呼......呼......我一听到消息就来了，这屋子怎么突然就倒了？！","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"画店店主","text":"绘匠人呢？那位来修复画作的客人呢？","id":397},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大胆的镇民","text":"别问了，还不快过来和我一起挖！","id":399},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担心的镇民","text":"来了来了，我带人来了。","id":401},{"type":"dialog","id":402},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.8","id":403},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":404},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":405},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":406},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":407},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大胆的镇民","text":"你有看到什么吗？","id":409},{"type":"character","name":"avg_NPC_460_1#1$1","name2":"avg_NPC_459_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"担心的镇民","text":"没有，你们呢？","id":411},{"type":"dialog","id":412},{"type":"character","id":413},{"type":"dia